Recipe for 16 leg and thigh pieces
| Ingredient                | Amount                 |
|---------------------------+------------------------|
| Garlic Paste              | 8 spoons               |
| Ginger Paste              | 6 spoons               |
| Kosher Salt OR Table Salt | 5 spoons OR 3.5 spoons |
| Ground Pepper             | andaj                  |
| Chili Powder              | 2 spoons               |
| Tandoori Powder (Laziza)  | 1 packet               |
| Lime Juice OR Whole Lime  | 3 spoons OR 2 halves   |
| EVOO                      | 2 spoons               |
| Mustard Oil               | 2 spoons               |
| Yogurt                    | 11 spoons              |
